                <note rend="inline" type="source">882.20/432: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Walton</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1939-03-16T20:00:00-05:00"
                            >March 16, 1939—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>6. Your 14, March 15, 3 p.m. Please forward via commercial cable in same code as
                    this message full text of the <hi rend="italic">aide-mémoire</hi> handed you by
                    the Secretary of State. After it has been received and studied, appropriate
                    instructions will be sent to you.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Welles</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
